item.title: Janeo add a quote by Winston S. Churchill
item.description: "Success is not final, failure is not fatal: it is the courage to continue that counts." -- Winston S. Churchill

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Theodore Roosevelt
item.description: "Do what you can, with what you have, where you are." -- Theodore Roosevelt

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Dan Zadra
item.description: "No one can go back and make a brand new start, my friend, but anyone can start from here and make a brand new end." -- Dan Zadra

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Mark Helprin
item.description: "As long as you have life and breath, believe. Believe for those who cannot. Believe even if you have stopped believing. Believe for the sake of the dead, for love, to keep your heart beating, believe. Never give up, never despair, let no mystery confound you into the conclusion that mystery cannot be yours." -- Mark Helprin

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Vince Lombardi
item.description: "once you learn to quit, it becomes a habit" -- Vince Lombardi

item.title: Janeo add a quote by William W. Purkey
item.description: "You've gotta dance like there's nobody watching, Love like you'll never be hurt, Sing like there's nobody listening, And live like it's heaven on earth." -- William W. Purkey

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Bob Ross
item.description: "We don't make mistakes, just happy little accidents." -- Bob Ross

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Bob Marley
item.description: "None but ourselves can free our minds." -- Bob Marley

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Martin Luther King Jr.
item.description: "Never, never be afraid to do what's right, especially if the well-being of a person or animal is at stake. Society's punishments are small compared to the wounds we inflict on our soul when we look the other way." -- Martin Luther King Jr.

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Lucille Ball
item.description: "Love yourself first and everything else falls into line. Your really have to love yourself to get anything done in this world." -- Lucille Ball

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Stephen Chbosky
item.description: "And in that moment, I swear we were infinite." -- Stephen Chbosky

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Stephen Chbosky
item.description: "So, I guess we are who we are for alot of reasons. And maybe we'll never know most of them. But even if we don't have the power to choose where we come from, we can still choose where we go from there. We can still do things. And we can try to feel okay about them." -- Stephen Chbosky

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Stephen Chbosky
item.description: "It's just that I don't want to be somebody's crush. If somebody likes me, I want them to like the real me, not what they think I am. And I don't want them to carry it around inside. I want them to show me, so I can feel it too." -- Stephen Chbosky

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Stephen Chbosky
item.description: "And I guess I realized at that moment that I really did love her. Because there was nothing to gain, and that didn't matter." -- Stephen Chbosky

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Stephen Chbosky
item.description: "We accept the love we think we deserve." -- Stephen Chbosky

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Marilyn Monroe
item.description: "I'm selfish, impatient and a little insecure. I make mistakes, I am out of control and at times hard to handle. But if you can't handle me at my worst, then you sure as hell don't deserve me at my best." -- Marilyn Monroe

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Albert Camus
item.description: "Don't walk behind me; I may not lead. Don't walk in front of me; I may not follow. Just walk beside me and be my friend." -- Albert Camus

item.title: Janeo add a quote by Martin Luther King Jr.
item.description: "Darkness cannot drive out darkness: only light can do that. Hate cannot drive out hate: only love can do that." -- Martin Luther King Jr.
